I enter the password "Test@123" in the input

I click on "CONTINUE" button

I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I skip linking my card

I click on "MAYBE LATER" button
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I click on "TRANSACTIONS" tab
I check no transactions on Transactions history screen
I check that the application text: "No transactions found" is equals to expected value: "No transactions found"
I click on "INVOICES" tab
I verify "No invoices Image" Icon
